            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7c7d5c39-a905-4129-9377-b37d4b1be6e0">
                Mr. A. C. Manuel  (Central Ayrshire)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7c7d5c39-a905-4129-9377-b37d4b1be6e0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-28/debates/7fc05ca2-a0e8-4be4-8cf4-0cd6a434eea5/TransportFareIncreases#contribution-7c7d5c39-a905-4129-9377-b37d4b1be6e0">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
