        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cadf833f-7985-4498-aba4-713702b4d058">
                Mr. Speaker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cadf833f-7985-4498-aba4-713702b4d058" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-28/debates/7fc05ca2-a0e8-4be4-8cf4-0cd6a434eea5/TransportFareIncreases#contribution-cadf833f-7985-4498-aba4-713702b4d058">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did hear the right hon. and learned Gentleman give a very general invitation to that side of the House, but I hope, in the interests of consecutive debate and good order, that they will not accept it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cadf833f-7985-4498-aba4-713702b4d058" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-04-28/debates/7fc05ca2-a0e8-4be4-8cf4-0cd6a434eea5/TransportFareIncreases#contribution-cadf833f-7985-4498-aba4-713702b4d058">
