<p class="">Is it £2½ million altogether or £2½ million plus London?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4d844582-5017-4925-9d58-4c73e48cd69d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
