        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">At whose expense?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8641ba05-2a7a-4816-8b51-3af4e5b4ee3d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
