            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7bcb330c-246f-47e5-a028-5d125091441e">
                Mr. G. H. Oliver  (Ilkeston)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7bcb330c-246f-47e5-a028-5d125091441e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
