        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The Consultative Committee gave a figure of 86 per cent., which is not the same as that given by London Transport.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-706121b3-f05a-45ca-ba76-710714c1b3e0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
