            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2fa4be82-11a9-4c71-b1bc-ee92b3b53123" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
